translations.name: English Jubilee 2000 Bible
translations.description: The Jubilee Bible 2000 is a study Bible complied by Russel Stendal, a Columnian missionary. Part Bible, part concordance, it attempts to use context to remove the need for outside reference materials. In order to do so, the usage of each word is tracked throughout the Bible. In the New Testament, the Hebrew equivalent to each Greek word is given.
